<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:qxa="urn:schemas-quark-com:xmlauthor" xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" author="Brandon Kiem" dateTime="2021-12-20T11:16:03" id="_3d207b06-4ef1-4897-af3b-bd718298b315" outputclass="ncc-clause" type="insert"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>S42C4</sptc><title id="_163ee7e4-f04d-4e26-92be-30ee54af5943">Additional Deemed-to-Satisfy Provisions when using house energy rating software</title><archive-num>3.12.0</archive-num><subclause id="_2ffda2c1-410f-4792-94d8-a8ec41ccdc7d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e9c1aacd-21d9-4712-b111-155a9e810a2b">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>To comply with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1946_3.17.0.xml#_ebeae85f-b094-4bad-a411-364a0334aa3b" id="_eda4e7d1-928b-48e6-b478-2aeef8e4acb2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">H6P1</xref>, in addition to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1953_3.29.0.xml#_9f1997aa-d81a-453a-ad0b-8f6681e8eaf0" id="_c5a3f77c-4426-4fef-bd98-decdd5473603" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">S42C2</xref>, a building must comply with Section 13 of the ABCB Housing Provisions clauses—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_edae1342-4234-4812-9755-4f3af0b4371d"><xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/2043#_e835680a-a71a-42c2-995e-0550abdf0eda" id="_2f7a44ac-27e7-4651-9947-5dd0cf095ff1" publishing-id="housing" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">13.2.2</xref>, for buildi