alse" type="standard-part">Part 13.4</xref>, for building sealing.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_7694c60b-d53e-4f27-8b59-62e09300cf78" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_bb4607ed-f82b-4f7d-850d-edf5417c873d">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>To comply with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1947_3.15.0.xml#_e8d2c621-96a1-44a3-a7e7-0bfd6b7ab184" id="_818a3d50-157d-431e-b4dd-82a8b3b4a92b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">H6P2</xref>, in addition to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/6272_0.9.0.xml#_da472c90-0099-4a3e-9739-3526a9379554" id="_b452afa6-f5ea-49be-a852-a991af4a73a1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">S42C3</xref>, a building must comply with <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/4236#_a63a0b59-83de-4c2b-8fad-bca5e858ad75" id="_b2d92268-6da7-4c81-bf42-fad547b14a6a" publishing-id="housing" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="standard-part">Part 13.7</xref> of the ABCB Housing Provisions.</p></subclause></clause>